HR

Welcome to

Team Management Services

TMS has been at the forefront of providing quality HR solutions to organizations through our onsite & offsite HR solutions. We are a team of experienced and trusted HR experts and we constantly strive to bring in new technologies & service offerings to the Human Resource domain. We ensure highest levels of satisfaction, efficiency as well as productivity.

  • 3,000+ employees

  • Servicing over 75 locations pan India

  • 100% statutory compliance

  • 99% customer satisfaction rate

Services


HR CONSULTING & ADVISORY
Our consulting & advisory practice helps clients set up effective HR processes for the growth of their organizations. From organizational restructuring to leadership coaching to labour advisory and turnkey HR projects, our experts provide diverse customized solutions to our clients.

Know More


3RD PARTY CONTRACT STAFFING
We provide need-based staffing solutions whether it is permanent staffing or temporary staffing. We fulfil the need for flexibility of workforce, productivity improvement and the growing legal compliance requirements through a combination of our vast experience and technological innovation.

Know More


HR OUTSOURCING
We provide complete HR outsourcing for mid & small-sized firms. Our solution covers a gamut services like payroll management, inductions, statutory compliance, leave & attendance, appraisals, organization structure design and many more.

Know More


TALENT ACQUISITION
We are one of the highest rated recruitment service providers in India. Our expertise ranges from campus recruitment to start up hiring to executive level search with the highest closure rate in mid to senior level mandates.
